软件包 fi.sorberIT

类摘要
HandleInformation HandleInformation is connected with the HibernateUtil class and MySAXHandler class.
HibernateUtil HibernateUtil is to initialize the configuration file--hibernate.cfg.xml and build a session factory, then open a session.It will be started when the project starts.
MySAXHandler MySAXHandler class is used to parse XML file by some specific methods and set attributes' value.
ReplaceXML ReplaceXML class is used to replace all the special characters in the xml file.
SaxParse SaxParse class is the main class, it's main use is to start the SAXParser.
